kthSmallestKey(node: AvlNode, k: Int)
1. k = 8
2. We start from N = 50.
3. N.size = 8 = N.left.size + 1 = 7 + 1 = k
4. So, if (k == N.left.size + 1) then return N
5. Otherwise, if (k < N.left.size + 1) then recursively call this function for (N.left, k)
6. And if (k > N.left.size + 1) then recursively call this function for (N.right, k - (N.left.size) - 1)
7. Dry run for other values of. For example, when k = 7, 9, or 15 for the given AVLTree.
